      • isComplete

        public boolean isComplete()
        Hillary: returns true or false depending on whether there are any empty slots on the bracket. If a position has an empty string then the advancing team has not been chosen for that spot and the whole bracket is not complete.
        Returns:
        boolean.

      • isSubtreeComplete

        public boolean isSubtreeComplete(int root)
        Hillary: returns true or false depending on whether there are any empty slots in te bracket from a given point all the way to the starting 64 teams. If the root itself is empty return false. otherwise the method is recursively applied to the left and right subtrees of the root.
        Parameters:
        root, - the int index of the root
        Returns:
        boolean update by matt and hillary 5/2
